Title: Struggle for Eagle Peak
Writer: Tancred Ibsen, A. Överland, Arnulf Øverland (play)
Actors: Alf Malland, Tor Stokke, Eva Bergh, Ingerid Vardund
Plot: Two old friends climbing the Eagle Peak mountain, reveals an intelligent story about a friend trying to get rid of another and getting revenge, take the glory of friend's achievement, get his leading job in the firm, and even his woman.
